casebody.data:
No. 10-7213. Connell Spain, Petitioner v. Texas Medical Board Disciplinary Committee. 562 U.S. 1105, 131 S. Ct. 850,

178 L. Ed. 2d 552,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 9665. December 13, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Texas dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
